{"tid":792982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高登記者正式道歉","createTime":"2018-08-25T04:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T05:03:01.000Z","uid":73915,"like":7,"dislike":304,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"4c51c759a4346ce23a71edd6e4dfd81cf6d6317d","tid":792982,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:01:09.000Z","msg":"本來收到爆料係準備認真出，只係整完片後覺得好似唔夠爆，擔心無辦法make noise，所以貪心整埋膠片，但結果最後令件事失左焦<br />\n<br />\n係到向各位巴打道歉，高登新聞一直以黎都係玩味性質為主，而且見觀眾都受落，所以誤判呢類題材加膠都無問題<br />\n<br />\n以後高登新聞係嚴肅話題上唔會再玩膠，會認真跟進<br />\n<br />\n再次為自己經驗不足對大家造成既滋擾道歉<br />\n<br />\n我明白道幾多次歉都好難平息巴打既不滿，但我保證將來會用返適當既方法處理適當既題材，希望唔會再令巴打失望<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對唔住各位"},{"pid":"b0dcbed687a3e316027110ffe461d484531e389e","tid":792982,"uid":5253,"like":92,"dislike":2,"score":90,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:06:21.000Z","msg":"叫牙祖出黎道歉"},{"pid":"cad79eb34af6f3c804f70b106a33c01838e26353","tid":792982,"uid":41116,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:07:07.000Z","msg":"趁地淋啦 林早洩"},{"pid":"dd5016ba5e23e76ecb2288317650092597102da5","tid":792982,"uid":188,"like":3,"dislike":33,"score":-30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"Skr"},{"pid":"0dc12d9d3c4f445c749dc404311b62a1252d2ba7","tid":792982,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b0dcbed687a3e316027110ffe461d484531e389e","tid":792982,"uid":5253,"like":92,"dislike":2,"score":90,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:06:21.000Z","msg":"叫牙祖出黎道歉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71d4ec2d92ad8fcebd8e0f470c939a089bf456b","tid":792982,"uid":2419,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"咩事先得架"},{"pid":"39dcefd3610d2ff59674cfa4efdecde39c4ad575","tid":792982,"uid":202464,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:19:36.000Z","msg":"乜有人